The paper proposes a novel approach to feature selection using mutual information and provides theoretical results to support their method. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions classification and regression, which are common tasks in Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Data Science (cs.DS). The paper also provides numerical simulations to support their claims, which suggests that it may also belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category.
